WEBVTT

00:02:29.299 --> 00:02:35.101
va ming yildan keyin afinaliklar 
suzib yurgan kema - 'B' kema bor.

00:02:35.101 --> 00:02:40.517
Endi biz juda oddiy savol beramiz: 
A kema B ga o'xshashmi?

00:02:40.517 --> 00:02:45.408
Kimdir ming yil davomida bitta Teseyning 
kemasi bor, deb javob beradi va u bilan

00:02:45.408 --> 00:02:48.493
bo'lgan barcha o'zgarishlar
asta-sekin sodir bo'lganligi sababli,

00:02:48.493 --> 00:02:53.667
afsonaviy kema hech qachon 
bor bo'lishdan to'xtamagan, deydi.

00:02:53.667 --> 00:02:56.267
Garchi ularning umumiy qismlari umuman 
yo'q bo'lsa-da,

00:02:56.267 --> 00:03:01.200
ikki kema bir xil - yani u bitta 
va yagonadir,